# Input

```css
.foo {
	@apply text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-600 accent-red accent-blue accent-green text-sm text-md hover:underline md:grid;
}

```


# Options

```json
{
  "css": {
    "parser": {
      "tailwindDirectives": true
    }
  }
}
```

# Formatted

```css
.foo {
	@apply text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-600 accent-red accent-blue accent-green text-sm text-md hover:underline md:grid;
}

```

# Lines exceeding max width of 80 characters
```
    2: 	@apply text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-600 accent-red accent-blue accent-green text-sm text-md hover:underline md:grid;
```
